  "title": "Junior Marketing Officer",
  "description": "<p>Euphoria Organization is seeking motivated individuals to join our growing team. This role offers structured training, performance-based career progression, and exposure to client-facing marketing campaigns.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Represent brands through face-to-face marketing</p></li><li><p>Engage customers using effective communication</p></li><li><p>Participate in team briefings and ongoing training</p></li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Merit-based promotions and uncapped earnings</p></li><li><p>One-to-one mentorship and professional development</p></li><li><p>Performance-based travel opportunities</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>No experience required; training provided</p></li><li><p>Strong communication skills and a growth mindset</p></li><li><p>Singaporeans or Permanent Residents only</p></li></ul>",
